Eels were long-bodied fish that were found on planets throughout the galaxy. Types of eel included the Colo claw fish of Naboo,[source?]
the Rishi eel of the Rishi Moon, the Mon Calamari eel of Mon Cala, the Armored eel of Yavin 4, the Omereth giant eel of Omereth, the Porthomer eel of Lew'el, the Purcassian river eel and a species on Quila.
